USAGE LICENSE  
Spineshatter EU PvP Extension Addon

1. **Overview**  
This agreement applies to the software tool known as the "Spineshatter EU PvP Extension Addon" (hereinafter referred to as "the Addon"). It is an extension of the **[Scambuster framework](https://github.com/hypernormalisation/Scambuster)** and compiles a list of offenders using publicly available data from the **[Spineshatter EU PvP Discord](https://discord.gg/spineshatter)**.

2. **Disclaimer**  
The Addon is provided “as is,” with no express or implied warranties regarding functionality or performance. It uses public data from the Spineshatter EU PvP Discord. The developers do not verify this data and make no claims about its accuracy or reliability. Use is at your own risk.

3. **No Affiliation**  
The Addon is not affiliated with or endorsed by the Spineshatter EU PvP Discord or its moderators. All data is public and not controlled or verified by the developers.

4. **Warranty**  
The Addon is provided without warranties of any kind. No guarantees are made regarding accuracy, compatibility, or uptime. The developers disclaim all warranties, including implied warranties of merchantability and fitness for a particular purpose.

